en_7706775_0	COLOMBO (News 1 st ): Three suspects have been arrested today (March 01) in Dematagoda while in possession of  Heroin.
en_7706775_1	Police had discovered 500 grams of Heroin which, according to Police Anti Narcotic Bureau, is worth over Rs.
en_7706775_2	6 Million.
en_7706775_3	The arrested suspects are residents of Moratuwa and Mattakkuliya, Police said.
en_7706775_4	Police added that the suspects will be produced before the Maligakanda Magistrates Court.
